## 6. Frontend Architecture Rules

Use:
- React.js
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Redux Toolkit
- RTK Query
- Clerk React SDK

Recommended frontend structure:

src/
  app/
    store.ts
    rootReducer.ts

  auth/
